how to use JOOQ.

1. add required plugins to pom and set up it for configs.

2. generate the source of jooq via maven lifecycle build -mvn clean install -DskipTests

3. add to build path the target source generated by jooq

4. use the jooq queries via DSLContext and use the table generated by jooq in your queries.
	place it in gateway layer.
5. deciding of the gateway to use(factory pattern), binding of data from record to model, model to record 
	is placed in repository layer.
	
6. business process is placed in service layer.

7. happy coding!